    <slider x="225" y="250" width="190" height="50" display="zombie-vision-radius" variable="zombie-vision-radius" min="1" max="20" default="6.0" step="1" direction="Horizontal"></slider>
    <slider x="225" y="305" width="190" height="50" display="simulation-speed" variable="simulation-speed" min="1" max="30" default="10.0" step="1" direction="Horizontal"></slider>

    <slider x="20" y="435" width="190" height="50" display="max-initial-rabbit-strength" variable="max-initial-rabbit-strength" min="0" max="10" default="3.0" step="0.1" direction="Horizontal"></slider>
    <slider x="20" y="490" width="190" height="50" display="rabbit-mutation-rate" variable="rabbit-mutation-rate" min="0" max="100" default="10.0" step="1" direction="Horizontal"></slider>
    <slider x="20" y="545" width="190" height="50" display="rabbit-mutation-ampl" variable="rabbit-mutation-ampl" min="0" max="1" default="0.2" step="0.05" direction="Horizontal"></slider>
    <slider x="225" y="435" width="190" height="50" display="zombie-mutation-rate" variable="zombie-mutation-rate" min="0" max="100" default="10.0" step="1" direction="Horizontal"></slider>
    <slider x="225" y="490" width="190" height="50" display="zombie-mutation-ampl" variable="zombie-mutation-ampl" min="0" max="1" default="0.2" step="0.05" direction="Horizontal"></slider>
    <slider x="225" y="545" width="190" height="50" display="delta-for-guaranteed-win" variable="delta-for-guaranteed-win" min="0" max="3" default="1.0" step="0.1" direction="Horizontal"></slider>

    <switch x="20" y="615" width="95" height="35" display="grass-ul?" variable="grass-ul?" on="true"></switch>
    <switch x="120" y="615" width="95" height="35" display="grass-ur?" variable="grass-ur?" on="true"></switch>
    <switch x="220" y="615" width="95" height="35" display="grass-ll?" variable="grass-ll?" on="true"></switch>
    <switch x="320" y="615" width="95" height="35" display="grass-lr?" variable="grass-lr?" on="true"></switch>

    <monitor x="1000" y="30" width="105" height="55" display="rabbits" precision="0" fontSize="11">count rabbits</monitor>
    <monitor x="1115" y="30" width="105" height="55" display="zombies" precision="0" fontSize="11">count zombie-rabbits</monitor>
    <monitor x="1230" y="30" width="115" height="55" display="infected grass" precision="0" fontSize="11">count patches with [pcolor = red]</monitor>
    <monitor x="1000" y="95" width="160" height="55" display="mean rabbit strength" precision="2" fontSize="11">ifelse-value any? rabbits [mean [strength] of rabbits] [0]</monitor>
    <monitor x="1170" y="95" width="170" height="55" display="mean zombie strength" precision="2" fontSize="11">ifelse-value any? zombie-rabbits [mean [strength] of zombie-rabbits] [0]</monitor>

    <plot x="1000" y="170" width="360" height="210" display="Population" xMin="0.0" xMax="10.0" yMin="0.0" yMax="200.0" autoPlotX="true" autoPlotY="true" legend="true">
      <setup></setup><update></update>
      <pen display="rabbits" interval="1.0" mode="0" color="-7500403" legend="true"><setup></setup><update>plot count rabbits</update></pen>
      <pen display="zombies" interval="1.0" mode="0" color="-5825686" legend="true"><setup></setup><update>plot count zombie-rabbits</update></pen>
    </plot>

    <plot x="1000" y="395" width="360" height="210" display="Mean strength" xMin="0.0" xMax="10.0" yMin="0.0" yMax="5.0" autoPlotX="true" autoPlotY="true" legend="true">
      <setup></setup><update></update>
      <pen display="rabbits" interval="1.0" mode="0" color="-7500403" legend="true"><setup></setup><update>plot ifelse-value any? rabbits [mean [strength] of rabbits] [0]</update></pen>
      <pen display="zombies" interval="1.0" mode="0" color="-5825686" legend="true"><setup></setup><update>plot ifelse-value any? zombie-rabbits [mean [strength] of zombie-rabbits] [0]</update></pen>
    </plot>

    <plot x="1000" y="620" width="360" height="210" display="Strength histogram" xMin="0.0" xMax="10.0" yMin="0.0" yMax="10.0" autoPlotX="false" autoPlotY="true" legend="true">
      <setup></setup><update></update>
      <pen display="rabbits" interval="0.1" mode="1" color="-7500403" legend="true"><setup></setup><update>histogram [strength] of rabbits</update></pen>
      <pen display="zombies" interval="0.1" mode="1" color="-5825686" legend="true"><setup></setup><update>histogram [strength] of zombie-rabbits</update></pen>
    </plot>
  </widgets>
  <info><![CDATA[## WHAT IS IT?

A NetLogo model for Lab 5 / RIA Lab 8: butterfly effect and co-evolution.
Rabbits eat grass. If they eat red infected grass, they become zombie-rabbits. Zombie-rabbits chase rabbits and attempt to infect them.

## HOW IT WORKS

Rabbits have energy and strength. Rabbits lose energy when moving, gain energy from green grass, reproduce probabilistically, and die when energy reaches zero.

Zombie-rabbits have energy and strength. They lose energy while moving and gain energy when they defeat a rabbit. If the rabbit wins the strength battle, the zombie dies. If the zombie wins, the rabbit becomes a zombie and inherits the zombie parent's strength, followed by mutation.

The four grass switches choose which quadrant receives an infected red patch during setup.

## HOW TO USE IT

Set the sliders, turn quadrant switches on/off, press setup, then go.

Important sliders:
- max-initial-rabbit-strength: random upper limit for rabbit strength at setup.
- rabbit/zombie mutation rate: probability of mutation.
- rabbit/zombie mutation ampl: maximum mutation size.
- delta-for-guaranteed-win: how large a strength gap is needed for guaranteed victory.

## THINGS TO NOTICE

Small changes in initial infected grass placement or mutation parameters can produce different long-term outcomes: rabbit survival, zombie dominance, collapse, or fluctuating equilibrium.
]]></info>
